    "content_license" : "CC BY-SA 3.0",
    "body" : "<pre><code>class Replacement \n{\n    public static void main(String args[])\n    {\n        String Main = \"5 * x^3 - 6 * x^1 + 1\";\n        String replaced = Main.replaceAll(\"(?m)(:?\\\\d+) \\\\* x\\\\^(:?\\\\d+)\", \"$1x&lt;sup&gt;$2&lt;/sup&gt;\");\n        System.out.println(replaced);\n    }\n}\n</code></pre>\n"
