    "content_license" : "CC BY-SA 3.0",
    "body" : "<pre><code>private String removeScript(String content) {\n    Pattern p = Pattern.compile(\"&lt;script[^&gt;]*&gt;(.*?)&lt;/script&gt;\",\n            Pattern.DOTALL | Pattern.CASE_INSENSITIVE);\n    return p.matcher(content).replaceAll(\"\");\n}\n</code></pre>\n"
